.
 The isomorphism is as limits of topological rings, and the unique isomorphism
 is induced by the projections 
\begin_inset Formula $p_{n}:\Z_{p}\to\Z/p^{n}\Z$
\end_inset

 defined by first quotienting by 
\begin_inset Formula $\Z_{p}/p^{n}\Z_{p}$
\end_inset

 and then exploiting the isomorphism between 
